# QP Megathread CODEOWNERS
# ------------------------------------------------------------
# This file restricts who can approve changes to certain paths.
# For CODEOWNERS to actually BLOCK merges you also need a branch
# protection rule on `main` with "Require review from Code Owners"
# enabled (Settings → Branches → Branch protection rules).
#
# The homepage and shared assets are locked to maintainers.
# Everything else (subpages, docs) is open for anyone to PR.
# ------------------------------------------------------------

# Lock the index and shared assets to maintainers
/index.html           @KaladinDMP
/assets/               @KaladinDMP
/CNAME                @KaladinDMP
/.github/             @KaladinDMP

# Subpages are intentionally NOT listed here so that anyone
# can contribute to them without a maintainer review.
# (/pages/** is open to the community.)
